The paper deals with signal recovery and restoration, which is a common topic in information theory (cs.IT) and signal processing (cs.SP). The paper also mentions applications such as image in-painting and super-resolution, which are typically covered in computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
